    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-08-01",
      "stem": "在 $\\odot O$ 中，直径 $CD \\perp$ 弦 $AB$ 于 $E$，则下列结论错误的是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$AE = BE$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$\\overset{\\frown}{AC} = \\overset{\\frown}{BC}$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$OE = DE$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$\\overset{\\frown}{AD} = \\overset{\\frown}{BD}$" }
      ],
      "answer": "C",
      "analysis": "由垂径定理，$AE = BE$，$\\overset{\\frown}{AC} = \\overset{\\frown}{BC}$，$\\overset{\\frown}{AD} = \\overset{\\frown}{BD}$ 都正确。但 $OE$ 和 $DE$ 不一定相等。",
      "source": "2023年深圳中考"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-08-02",
      "stem": "$\\odot O$ 的半径为 $5$，弦 $AB = 8$，则圆心 $O$ 到弦 $AB$ 的距离为（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$3$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$4$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$5$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$6$" }
      ],
      "answer": "A",
      "analysis": "过 $O$ 作 $OC \\perp AB$，$AC = 4$，$OC = \\sqrt{5^2 - 4^2} = 3$。",
      "source": "2022年深圳中考"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice",
